text: Nasser Shabani (; died 13 March 2020) was an Iranian general. He was a senior commander of Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps (IRGC). He took credit for using Houthi rebels to target Saudi oil tankers. == Death == Shabani died of coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) on 13 March 2020. == References == Category:Year of birth missing Category:2020 deaths Category:Iranian generals Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Iran
